CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1773609114
OL,3,C'Standing up for values at home and
OL,4,Cabroad is important' - Naomi Long
OL,6,FMrs Long began her speech by thanking
OL,7,FMr Burnham for his attendance.
OL,9,FShe said: "As someone from a northern
OL,10,Findustrial town, who grew up in a two-
OL,11,Fup two-down that opened straight out
OL,12,Fonto the street, I wonder if some of
OL,13,Fthose in power are worried about the
OL,14,Fpower they would unlock if people like
OL,15,Fus actually got our hands on some of
OL,16,Fthe power that they like to hang on
OL,17,Fto."
OL,26,@qD@KOUyD@DO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
