OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1773609114
OL,3,C'Standing up for values at home and
OL,4,Cabroad is important' - Naomi Long
OL,6,FMrs Long reflected on 25 years since
OL,7,Fshe was first elected and almost 10
OL,8,Fyears since she became party leader,
OL,9,Fbefore criticising US President Donald
OL,10,FTrump and warning the Alliance Party's
OL,11,Fplace in the powersharing Executive
OL,12,Fshould not be taken for granted.
OL,14,FMrs Long made similar comments during
OL,15,Fan interview with the Press
OL,16,FAssociation during the week, where she
OL,17,Fsaid she would step away from the
OL,18,FExecutive if she believed that it had
OL,19,Fbecome too "threadbare" to deliver for
OL,20,Fpeople.
OL,26,@{D@LOU{D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
