OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1773609114
OL,3,C'Standing up for values at home and
OL,4,Cabroad is important' - Naomi Long
OL,6,FSpeaking on Saturday, she pledged she
OL,7,Fwould not to "stand by" as progress
OL,8,Fwas frustrated and that she was
OL,9,Fconfident her party was "best-placed
OL,10,Fto lead us forward".
OL,12,F"As someone who grew up during the
OL,13,FTroubles, I will never take our
OL,14,Fprogress for granted, but equally I
OL,15,Fwill also not stand by while others
OL,16,Frest on their laurels or frustrate
OL,17,Fprogress," Mrs Long said.
OL,26,@oD@NOUoD@WO]qD@YOUrD@SO]tD@AOUyD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1773609114
OL,3,C'Standing up for values at home and
OL,4,Cabroad is important' - Naomi Long
OL,6,FShe said that if they reach a point
OL,7,Fwhere the party's key priorities are
OL,8,F"stymied by vetoes and frustrated by
OL,9,Fheel-dragging", then she would be
OL,10,F"advocating a change in direction".
OL,12,F"Our continued participation in the
OL,13,FExecutive cannot and should not be
OL,14,Ftaken for granted."
OL,16,FMrs Long said Alliance were an
OL,17,F"optimistic" party and that the
OL,18,Fprogress made by Northern Ireland to
OL,19,Fdate had been built on "hope, not
OL,20,Ffear".
OL,26,@pD@AOUqD@NO]rD@AOUrD@bO]tD@AOUvD@SO]yD@
OL,26,AAOUyD@LO]{D@XOU|D@EO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
