CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1773609114
OL,3,C'Standing up for values at home and
OL,4,Cabroad is important' - Naomi Long
OL,6,FShe said the party had proved its
OL,7,Fcritics "wrong" to become the third
OL,8,Flargest party in Stormont and said
OL,9,Fthey would not "entertain their
OL,10,Fcounsel of doom".
OL,12,F"Of course, there will always be those
OL,13,Fwho seek to talk down our achievements
OL,14,For suggest that our progress is
OL,15,Funsustainable.
OL,26,@oD@IOUoD@OO]qD@POUrD@PO]tD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1773609114
OL,3,C'Standing up for values at home and
OL,4,Cabroad is important' - Naomi Long
OL,6,F"What they have failed to grasp every
OL,7,Ftime is that Alliance success isn't
OL,8,Fmerely a party political phenomenon:
OL,9,Fit reflects the positive and
OL,10,Fprogressive change happening outside
OL,11,Frooms like these, in our communities."
OL,13,FIn relation to international affairs,
OL,14,FMrs Long said the party was not
OL,15,Fattending the White House for St
OL,16,FPatrick's Day celebrations as Mr Trump
OL,17,Fis someone who "engages in race-
OL,18,Fbaiting" and calls female journalists
OL,19,F"piggy".
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@fO]yD@POUzD@HO]{D@AOU{D@GO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/12
