PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1773609114
OL,3,C'Standing up for values at home and
OL,4,Cabroad is important' - Naomi Long
OL,6,F"As someone who believes in democracy,
OL,7,Ffreedom and peace, why would I want to
OL,8,Fspend time with someone who threatens
OL,9,Fthe global order and stability?" she
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,F"As someone whose family fought in the
OL,13,FSecond World War, why would I want to
OL,14,Fengage a man who so disgracefully
OL,15,Fdisrespected war veterans and
OL,16,Fcontinues to threaten US traditional
OL,17,Fallies?
OL,19,F"Trump may not have standards: we do."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@`O]tD@AOU{D@AOU{D@fO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/12
