OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1773609114
OL,3,C'Standing up for values at home and
OL,4,Cabroad is important' - Naomi Long
OL,6,FShe said it was important that the
OL,7,Fparty "speak up and speak out for"
OL,8,Ftheir values at home and abroad, and
OL,9,Fwarned against viewing "every
OL,10,Finternational conflict through the
OL,11,Flens of our local divisions" in
OL,12,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,14,FShe said the lack of "meaningful"
OL,15,Fsanctions for Russia's breaches of
OL,16,Finternational law in Ukraine had
OL,17,F"paved the way for further illegal
OL,18,Fwars" and that the US and Israel
OL,19,F"waging a war of choice on Iran" had
OL,20,Fserious implications for the world.
OL,26,@oD@GOUoD@bO]qD@XOUsD@\O]vD@VOUvD@aO]yD@
OL,26,AAOUzD@EO]{D@AOU{D@`O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/12
