OL,3,C'Standing up for values at home and
OL,4,Cabroad is important' - Naomi Long
OL,6,FShe said it was "simplistic and crass"
OL,7,Fto expect people to "pick a side" on
OL,8,Fconflicts as if it was a sport or game.
OL,26,@nD@QOUnD@fO]oD@UOUoD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/12
