OL,3,C'Standing up for values at home and
OL,4,Cabroad is important' - Naomi Long
OL,6,FShe said: "We need to articulate that,
OL,7,Fjust as it is possible both to agree
OL,8,Fthat Hamas are a terrorist regime and
OL,9,Fthat that Israeli government is
OL,10,Fengaged in genocide; it is possible to
OL,11,Fabhor the human rights abuses, murders
OL,12,Fand oppression of opponents by the
OL,13,FIranian regime whilst also
OL,14,Facknowledging the recent military
OL,15,Faction by the US and Israel is
OL,16,Fcontrary to international law, as are
OL,17,Fthe random retaliatory strikes by
OL,18,FIran."
OL,26,@nD@KOUzD@FO]
